            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1501681596,
            "creation_date": 1501681596,
            "body": "<p>what about using the <code>.<\/code> specifier?<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>myCollection.updateOne(Document.parse(\"{ \\\"_id\\\" : ObjectId(\\\"4f39805d35919a2a7c7aba3e\\\")}\"),\n    Document.parse(\"{$set:{ \\\"mouseLoc.x\\\" : \"+mouseX+\", \\\"mouseLoc.y\\\" : \"+mouseY+\" }\")\n)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 45462718,
            "question_id": 9268753
        }
